OL,3,CMan dies and woman seriously injured
OL,4,Cin Birmingham Queensway collision
OL,6,FA man in his 20s has died and a woman
OL,7,Fhas suffered potentially life-
OL,8,Fthreatening injuries after a car hit
OL,9,Frailings on Birmingham's Great Charles
OL,10,FStreet Queensway.
OL,12,FDrivers were being warned of long
OL,13,Ftraffic jams heading into the city
OL,14,Fcentre this morning (Monday, July 13).
OL,16,FWest Midlands Police says it was
OL,17,Fcalled just after 2.35am to the scene,
OL,18,Fat the junction of Great Charles
OL,19,FStreet Queensway and St Chad's
OL,20,FQueensway.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
