PN,34202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1783956016
OL,3,CMan dies and woman seriously injured
OL,4,Cin Birmingham Queensway collision
OL,6,FInvestigators remained at the scene
OL,7,Ffor a number of hours with the
OL,8,Fcarriageway closed off in both
OL,9,Fdirections until around 9am for
OL,10,Fexaminations of the scene and initial
OL,11,Fenquiries to be carried out.
OL,13,FDespite the best efforts of medics,
OL,14,Fthe driver was pronounced dead at the
OL,15,Fscene.
OL,17,FA woman, who was the sole passenger,
OL,18,Fwas treated by paramedics and taken to
OL,19,Fhospital for injuries which are
OL,20,Fpotentially life-threatening.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
