OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1783956016
OL,3,CMan dies and woman seriously injured
OL,4,Cin Birmingham Queensway collision
OL,6,FInvestigations to establish exactly
OL,7,Fwhat happened are on-going, but at
OL,8,Fthis stage, officers do not believe
OL,9,Fany other vehicles were involved.
OL,11,FSpecialist officers are asking anyone
OL,12,Fwho has dashcam footage from around
OL,13,Fthe time of the collision to get in
OL,14,Ftouch.
OL,16,FPolice say witnesses are being spoken
OL,17,Fwith and anyone who is yet to speak
OL,18,Fwith police is also asked to get in
OL,19,Fcontact.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
