OL,6,FAnyone with information can call
OL,7,Fpolice on 101, message via Live Chat,
OL,8,For email the Serious Collision
OL,9,FInvestigation Unit at
OL,10,FSCIU@westmidlands.police.uk, quoting
OL,11,Fthe log 384 of 13 July.
